
### 注册新用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/account/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "arch3@test.com",
  "password": "a12345678",
  "confirmPassword": "a12345678"
}


### 登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/account/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "arch3@test.com",
  "password": "a12345678"
}

### 刷新 token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/account/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 获取用户列表（分页，第 1 页，每页 20 条）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取用户列表（第 2 页）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?page=2&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 更新用户（id 从路径参数传入）
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "email": "updated@test.com"
}

### 删除用户（id 从路径参数传入）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
